<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Shaluk</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-02 16:01:46</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just a wizard's viewpoint on this place.. Lvl 32 wiz here and I've been in Dalnir solid for the last four or five days. Had a buddy call me over screaming about awesome loot and I'll give him this, he was definately right.. Exp is great at this lvl, but hazardous to get while solo. (Can take the Kly evokers and such out, but the coerced iksar and Erud's still kick the snot outta me.)  With a good group you can pretty much rock the place and mobs are readily available for pulling from whatever floor your on.  Word of caution: As it has been said, some of the goo's and nibbler's will agro, though the percentage is more like 20-30% from what I've seen. Invis is highly needed till second floor pool room and then from there as long as you stick to main tunnels you will be pretty much fine. (Side rooms contain the Imp and a couple of coerced on the way to portal room) Third floor is outstanding, actually a bit more open than the second floor with more room to Root, blast, and root again. ; ) I highly recommend any monks to go there as I've prolly let at least three suits of crescent decay with no monks in zone =(. Ya'll take care and I'll see you in Dalnir.<BR>
<BR>
Shaluk Twistedwit<BR>
Wizard of the 32 Circle<BR>
Bertoxx</font></td></tr></table>
